<Legal
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Kixlogic collects, uses, and protects personal information for customers and job applicants."
>
  <p>This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Kixlogic, LLC</strong> ("Kixlogic," "we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and shares information about you when you use our applicant tracking system and related services (the "Service").</p>

  <p>Kixlogic serves two types of people: <strong>Customers</strong> (businesses that subscribe to use Kixlogic) and <strong>Applicants</strong> (individuals who submit employment applications through a Kixlogic-powered careers page). This policy addresses both.</p>

  <div class="callout">If you are a job applicant submitting an application through a company's careers page powered by Kixlogic, the company you are applying to (not Kixlogic) is primarily responsible for how your application data is used. Please also review that company's privacy policy.</div>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <h3>From Customers</h3>
  <p>When you create and manage a Kixlogic account, we collect account information, billing details (processed by Stripe — we do not store full card numbers), company settings, usage data, and support communications.</p>

  <h3>From Applicants</h3>
  <p>When an individual submits a job application through a Kixlogic-powered careers page, we collect on behalf of the hiring company: name, contact information, employment history, resume documents, work eligibility, and voluntarily submitted EEO data.</p>

  <h3>Automatically Collected</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>IP address and general geographic location</li>
    <li>Browser type and version</li>
    <li>Pages visited and features used</li>
    <li>Date and time of access</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>Customer information is used to provide and improve the Service, process payments, send transactional emails, provide support, and comply with legal obligations.</p>
  <p>Applicant information is stored and displayed to the hiring company's authorized recruiters, used to power AI features on eligible plans, and used to send application confirmation emails.</p>
  <p>EEO data is collected separately, compartmentalized, and accessible only to Admin-level users for compliance reporting. It is never included in exports or AI scoring.</p>

  <h2>3. How We Share Information</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share information only as described below:</p>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Recipient</th><th>What is shared</th><th>Why</th></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Stripe</strong></td><td>Payment and billing information</td><td>Subscription payment processing</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Cloudflare</strong></td><td>Service traffic and application data</td><td>Application hosting and delivery</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Supabase</strong></td><td>Customer and applicant data</td><td>Encrypted database hosting</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Anthropic</strong></td><td>Resume and job description content</td><td>AI features on eligible plans</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Hiring companies</strong></td><td>Applicant application data</td><td>Transmitted to the company the applicant applied to</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Law enforcement</strong></td><td>As required by law</td><td>Legal process and government requests</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Customer account data:</strong> Duration of subscription plus 90 days after termination</li>
    <li><strong>Applicant data:</strong> While the hiring company's account is active plus 90 days after termination</li>
    <li><strong>Billing records:</strong> 7 years per tax and accounting requirements</li>
    <li><strong>Support communications:</strong> 2 years</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Request earlier deletion at <a href="mailto:support@kixlogic.com">support@kixlogic.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>TLS 1.2+ encryption for data in transit</li>
    <li>Encrypted database connections with encryption at rest</li>
    <li>Infrastructure hosted on Cloudflare and Supabase (U.S.)</li>
    <li>Role-based access controls and audit logging</li>
    <li>Server-side validated session tokens</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Customers can view and update account information in dashboard settings, manage billing through Stripe, and request deletion by contacting support.</p>
  <p>Applicants should contact the hiring company directly for access, correction, or deletion requests. We will assist in directing requests to the appropriate party.</p>

  <h2>7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
  <p>We use minimal browser storage for authenticated sessions and interface preferences. We do not use cross-site tracking, behavioral profiling, or third-party advertising trackers on kixlogic.com.</p>

  <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>The Service is not directed at individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect information from minors.</p>

  <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated by email or website notice at least 30 days before taking effect.</p>

  <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@kixlogic.com">support@kixlogic.com</a></li>
    <li><strong>Company:</strong> Kixlogic, LLC — Alexander City, Alabama</li>
  </ul>
</Legal>
